  tutorials:
  - The amount of Cash you have is represented on top right
  - The banana represents the energy you have
  - The energy bar depletes with time, you don't have all day to pick up trash!
  - Collect trash in the trash can... hover your mouse over the trash and that's
    it!
  - The trash looks like this...Now go!
